### Search
POST {{base}}/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "Kern",
  "k": 3
}

### Fetch (ID aus Search einsetzen)
POST {{base}}/fetch
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "PASTE_CHUNK_ID_HERE"
}

